  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic Tibial Tray CFD Credibility Assessment (NC-4 Clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite-element prediction of tibial tray stress distribution under physiological loading for a Class II orthopedic knee implant. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict peak von Mises stress and displacement fields within acceptance tolerances at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are assessed with achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across material property and boundary condition inputs. Decision: Accepted.",
