      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive model selected for CoCr tray (appropriate given strains remain below 0.1% yield strain under all loading scenarios). Bone represented as transversely isotropic linear elastic with properties assigned from CT-derived density-modulus relationships. Contact between tray and cement modelled with frictional Coulomb contact (μ=0.3). Model form assumptions documented and justified with reference to published literature and sensitivity analysis results.",
